	<p>We are so excited to celebrate our wedding with you in Arêches! We understand getting to France is a big adventure for everyone so here are some links to help you organize your trip.</p>
	<p><strong>Getting to France from the US</strong></p>
	<p>You can fly into to either Paris Roissy Charles de Gaulles (CDG) or Geneva Internation Airport (GVA). </p>
	<p><strong>From Paris</strong></p>
	<p>If you fly into Paris, you can take a train to Albertville. You can reserve train tickets here <a href="http://en.voyages-sncf.com/" target="_blank">http://www.voyages-sncf.com/</a>. From Albertville, there are shuttles to the town of Arêches, here is a <a href="http://www.areches-beaufort.com/admin/pdf/cars/horaires-car.pdf" target="_blank">link to the shuttle company</a>, you do not need to reserve this shuttle in advance. Or you can rent a car near the train station in Albertville.<br/></p>
